A Mexican Drug War-related march inspired by the killing of seven people, one of whom was the son of prominent poet and journalist Javier Sicilia, occur in more than 20 Mexican cities, with marchers chanting "No more blood!". (BBC)(LA Times)NATO kills 14 civilians, 12 children and 2 women, with an airstrike on homes in Helmand Province. (BBC) (Al Jazeera)